name: Educational Psychology Student Organization
description: To support graduate students in the EPSY department by representing the student body to faculty, planning social events and enrichment events. The purpose of this organization is to serve as a liaison between the graduate students and faculty members of the department of educational psychology serve as a source of information for graduate students promote social activities involving both graduate students and faculty members promote participation in professional activities and impact departmental, college, and University policies affect EPSY graduate students.
